page.title: 08HOME
page.content: My name is Victoria Keith.I live with my mum, dad and my brother Jason in a big granite house on the South Road on the outskirts of Peterhead.The house was built around the year 1885.The house has 10 old fashioned rooms.It has a big garden that is fun to play in.On one side of the house is a tarmacadam play area.On the side there is a field leading to the beach and behind the house across a field is Meethill Tower.The prison is along the road from our house which once belonged to Prison Authorities.Our neighbours are called the Leslies.Yvonne is my friend.There is not a lot of children in my area because most of the houses have older people in them,but I still love where I live.
